<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=84 g=1 f=1 -->
Nonattainment Area Requirements as They Pertain to Maryland 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
The Clean Air Act requirements under section 182, as they pertain to new sources in Maryland, specify that major sources
in the Baltimore severe ozone nonattainment area (Baltimore City, Baltimore, Anne Arundel, Carroll, Harford, and
