risk by transferring assets with low levels of recourse. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
&bull;The capital assessment rate does not recognize the difference in risk of loss between recourse or direct credit
substitutes that absorb first losses and recourse or direct credit substitutes that absorb second losses from the
underlying assets. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
