underlying assets; 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(iv) Assets sold under an agreement to repurchase; and 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
