<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=21 g=1 f=1 -->
 To calculate the risk-weighted asset amount for a recourse arrangement that is an on-balance sheet asset, multiply
the amount of assets from which risk of loss is directly or indirectly retained by the appropriate risk weight using
the criteria regarding obligors, guarantors, and collateral listed in section 3(a) of this appendix A. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(2) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=21 g=1 f=3 -->
